snippet.title: Ship of Harkinian Direct - 2022-03-22
snippet.description:
Tune in for roughly 5 minutes of information focused on features available in the next 10 days for the Ship of Harkinian, and a sneak peak at features that will be available in the coming months after launch.

Visit us on Discord
https://discord.gg/BtBmd55HVH
